.PP
To generate a report for inbound traffic from Abilene based on customer type:
.sp
.nf
flow-cat \fIflows\fR | flow-filter -i25 | flow-tag -t gigapop-tags -TOHIO-GIGAPOP | flow-xlate -T0xFF0000 | flow-stat -n -f31 -S2
.sp
.fi
